WEBVTT

00:11:28.988 --> 00:11:30.326
da bo dolgoročna rast bližje

00:11:30.326 --> 00:11:32.562
enemu do dvema odstotkoma

00:11:32.562 --> 00:11:35.110
in ne štirim ali petim.

00:11:35.110 --> 00:11:37.393
Poglejte tole,

00:11:37.393 --> 00:11:38.919
to so najboljše ocene

00:11:38.919 --> 00:11:40.446
svetovne rasti BDP-ja

00:11:40.446 --> 00:11:42.907
ter stopnje donosa na kapital,

00:11:42.907 --> 00:11:44.853
povprečne stopnje donosa,

00:11:44.853 --> 00:11:46.552
in vidite lahko, da je bila

00:11:46.552 --> 00:11:47.440
večino zgodovine

00:11:47.440 --> 00:11:48.788
stopnja rasti zelo nizka,

00:11:48.788 --> 00:11:51.285
mnogo nižja od stopnje donosa,

00:11:51.285 --> 00:11:52.908
v 20. stoletju

00:11:52.908 --> 00:11:55.502
pa sta rast prebivalstva,

00:11:55.502 --> 00:11:57.924
visoka predvsem v povojnem obdobju,

00:11:57.924 --> 00:11:59.715
ter proces obnove

00:11:59.715 --> 00:12:00.997
pripeljala rast